{
  "stem": "13457.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The name of the place was Guzar.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's not that exactly it was a place because it was a place in the middle of the nowhere.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a place in the middle of a desert, not sand desert, but windswept, dry desert.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that is where my father came to enlist in the Polish army that was then organizing to leave Russia through the Caspian Sea and go to Persia and then fight the war against the Germans in Italy.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The only problem was that [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the fucking Poles didn't forget their feelings about the Jews, and that was a handicap.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they were not taking Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were not taking Jews into the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were flatly denying the-- any kind of admission.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The soldiers, I mean the enlisted men, they certainly didn't take.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So then it came to it that my father came up with a true story that in 1921, towards the end of the First World War, my father was enlisted in the then new Polish army to fight the Bolsheviks because he was just a medical student, and he was then running some transport train.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he told it to these Polish officers in south of Russia and they took him into the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I think I'll finish this tape now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "No?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Yes?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We have a few more minutes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So then what happened, we were sitting in this little place in the middle of the nowhere starving.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We lived in one tent I would say 20 by 20 feet, about four Jewish families-- again, families of Jewish doctors.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and we're all dying from disease and from starvation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father had typhoid fever.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
